import '../app.css'; function Experience() { return (
{/* Experience*/}

Experience

Software Developer

Integrity Support, Inc.

Worked in a sophisticated MVC/MVVM .NET Pattern EHR application. Engaged in both front-end and back-end development using C#, Classic ASP, and Javascript to enhance user experiences. Crafted stored procedures and scripts in Microsoft SQL Server for efficient customer data management. Innovatively optimized SQL table structures by implementing custom arrays with JSON and jQuery. Created a cutting-edge client portal website with integrated chat, signature-capturing, and document-sharing functionalities, ensuring compliance with modern EHR regulations. Successfully deployed and tested using Azure CI/CD tools on Cloud Services with Microsoft IIS sites on a cloud Windows Server.

March 2022 - January 2024

Tutor

edX / 2U

Instructed over 100 students in the foundational principles of full-stack web development. Covered a spectrum of topics, spanning fundamental elements like HTML, CSS, and Javascript, to advanced skills such as constructing client-side applications utilizing third-party APIs through Fetch Calls. Additionally, provided comprehensive guidance on both MySQL and NoSQL databases, emphasizing the utilization of back-end Node JS technologies like Sequelize and Mongoose. The ultimate objective was to equip students with the proficiency to implement React in developing sophisticated MERN stack single-page applications (MongoDB, Express JS, React JS, Node JS).

May 2022 - January 2024

Insurance Sales Representative

Bankers Life

Financial Planning towards Retirement for all ages. Managed everything from health and medication costs, and planning for convalesent care. Also aided in estate and financial planning, working one-on-one with clients and their families both in-person and virtually.

January 2020 - July 2021

Videographer

East Carolina University - CRW Marketing & Promotion

Created visual content for their Campus Recreational and Wellness Department of the student facilities, club and intramural sports, and on campus Physical Trainers.

September 2019 - December 2019

Cheif Financial Officer

Lotus Experience on Demand Marketing Firm

Aided in logistics and promotion of events statewide through North Carolina. Created visual content and lead an executive staff of employees, independent contracters. Helped grow local businesses and individuals.

May 2017 - August 2019

Radio Station Production Manager

East Carolina University - WZMB 91.3

Created, edited, and recorded radio station promotional material, grant acknowledgements, and public service announcements for the University. Aided and trained classes of radio personel on basic radio production and FCC laws.

May 2016 - December 2017
); } export default Experience;
